<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:yellow;">'Stop It!'</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> she said to herself brusquely as she reached down to finish nursing her three month old daughter Lea. She had this one and the others to think about now. It was not the time to panic; and she would not allow herself to do that. No, she was her father's daughter and she would not panic.<br>
<br>
The small shuttle had taken heavy battle damge and she had to find another of the survivors of the last attack that had sent them fleeing. She just had to, and fast! She placed the now sleeping infant in the basket that was securely fastened to the support behind her pilot's chair and called for the baby's sister Valeria to assist her. <br>
<br>
They would find the assistance they needed before the shuttle broke up. They would survive, no other outcome was acceptable.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bslipstreambbs12353.showUserPublicProfile?gid=anastashia>Anastashia</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.e-cadfael.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/images/Page_6/565.jpg" BORDER=0> at: 2/28/03 8:55:01 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003B75><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bslipstreambbs12353.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lt@slipstreambbs12353>LT</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table style='Filter: Glow(Color=#de2fae, Strength=2)'><tr><td><span class='usertitle'>I just came for the cookies</span></td></tr></table></span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#EFD68C>(2/28/03 1:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=40>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: The Displaced ~ Tyrant RP (Rated R)</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:gray;font-size:x-small;">LT looked up as Sunyata spoke. &quot;Thank you for the compliment.&quot; She said smiling. &quot;I have to get away from the uniforms every now and then, what do you expect from a clothing designer?&quot; She added, grinning wryly. &quot;You could probably use a few tailored things yourself, a change from uniforms, if you please.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I have just received confirmation from all who were invited, they should be here shortly. I can't wait to see Sca. We were very close, like sisters.&quot; She told Sunyata. &quot;I don't know how many of them will bring their children, but Terri has everything ready, just in case.&quot;<br>
<br>
Finishing her report, she excuses herself to go see Orion one more time before dinner. She needed some time to think, to work through the memories of that last time before they left Idun. She had helped Sca train the teenagers and she led one band, and Sca had led the others. Though they all fought well, they were no match for the Argonas. She had been lucky enough not to have been seriously wounded before her small band had perished and had made her way to the freighter after bidding XT goodbye. Terri was already there with Orion, waiting for her and they had taken off. They took a hit from an Argona fighter before it was destroyed by one of the Tyrants. They had been able to slipstream, but they had developed a leak and were losing life support. Shutting down all unnecessary functions, she was able to extend their time before losing all life support entirely, Then the Hetupratyaya had tractored them into its cargo bay before she, Orion and Terri had suffocated. Luckily, none of them had any permanent damage from the lack of oxygen.<br>
<br>
Holding her son and rocking him, she thought about Sunyata's rescuing them. She didn't think there was any ulerior motive in her actions, LT had nothing that the woman would want, at least she didn't thinks so.<br>
<br>
That was one of the reasons that LT figured that they could trust Sunyata, she had never observed any underhanded behavior from her, but being naturally reserved, had still been cautious about trusting her implicitely.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bslipstreambbs12353.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lt@slipstreambbs12353>LT</A> at: 2/28/03 5:47:51 am<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=13.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showMessageRange?topicID=13.topic&start=41&stop=49>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=13.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showNextMessage?topicID=13.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.emailToFriend?topicID=13.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.threadControl?topicID=13.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fslipstreambbs12353frm12.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email